D3 Security System Add-on

-------------------------------------------------------
## Introduction:

This add-on facilitates the communication of events data between Splunk and D3 Incident response platform. 

-------------------------------------------------------
## Installation and Setup

- In Splunk, navigate to the app manager page. Click "Install app from file" and upload the D3 Add-on.
- Navigate to app manager page, click "Set up" on "D3 Cyber Incident Response Add-on" row. Fill out all configuration settings and click "Save". 

-------------------------------------------------------
